sentences: Christopher George Manak (born October 8, 1969 ), better known by his stage name Peanut Butter Wolf, is an American disc jockey and record producer from San Jose, California.
He is based in Los Angeles, where he moved to in 2000.
In 1989, Peanut Butter Wolf met rapper Charizma.
In 2010, Jeff Weiss of Los Angeles Times called it "a crate-digging classic that remains one of the seminal statements of the underground golden era."
